SUMMARY:Yom HaShoah Interfaith Remembrance (Offsite)
DESCRIPTION:All are welcome to join the annual interfaith Yom HaShoah Holocaust Commemoration\, hosted by the Montclair Interfaith Clergy Association. \n  \nAs part of the service\, we will hear from Pamela Romanchuk\, granddaughter of four Holocaust survivors\, who will share her family’s stories of survival\, family\, legacy\, and the enduring strength of the Jewish People.
URL:https://www.unioncong.org/event/yom-hashoah-interfaith-remembrance-offsite/
LOCATION:Temple B’nai Keshet\, 99 S Fullerton Ave\, Montclair\, NJ\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:All Events,Featured Events
END:VEVENT
