SUMMARY:Union Cong Bell Choir Rehearsal (Sanctuary)
DESCRIPTION:Our handbell ensemble is an eclectic\, fun\, and supportive group of musicians who love creating music that lifts our spirits\, challenges our creativity\, and provides moments of contemplation. All skill levels welcome. If you can count to four\, you can play handbells!
